4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t m46 x98 h4a y102d ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventist Review. </div><div class="t m192a x26 h2d y14af ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Elder and Mrs. Holbrook have three adult children. </div><div class="t m826 x26 haf y8aa ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check with your local Adventist Book </div><div class="t mcdc x26 haf y142f ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Center for the companion book to the Sab-</div><div class="t m28a x26 haf y10a6 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bath School Lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
